metadata.name: PLANCHE #1
metadata.description:
Planche #1, Projection du Cosmos

ATLAS is a series of compositions made with descriptions of historical and cosmographical images borrowed from Aby Warburg's Mnemosyne Atlas. Individual images are generated with a version of VQGAN+CLIP and processed with different post-production tools. 

The wallet that controls this asset also owns the individual images of this composition.
